>\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>效用－＞</ins></span></strong><br />\n1. 減少浪費時間 於 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無無謂謂</strong></span> 既 會員 張貼 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無無謂謂既 Post</strong></span><br />\n2. 阻嚇一下 張貼 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>膠Post</strong></span>，提高會員質素<br />\n3. 。。。。應該仲有好處。。。懶得打<br />\n<br />\n<strong>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 以下涉及IT技術層面，唔明白既請 SKIP &lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</strong><strong><br />\n如何實行－＞</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聲明</strong></span> : 只是研究作用為主，並不是強求要做，<br />\n<br />\n首先大家都明白，<span style=\"color: navy;\">實時更新是不設實際 或 不合效能</span><br />\n理論上，其實只需要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每隔一段時間 或 半夜，再行 Cron job 一批批 更新就好了</span></span></strong>，<br />\n大家其實只需要知道 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">Post主 歷史行為的總正負評數目</span></span></strong>，而 <span style=\"color: red;\">P</span> 可知道是否老屎忽，  <br />\n雖然可以使用起底，但實在太浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外：<br />\n相信大家都望到我大大個 <span style=\"color: red;\">P</span> 字，而亦都係<span style=\"color: red;\">第一個 Post</span>，<br />\n我只希望<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登管理員</span></strong>望到建議，<br />\n至於佢地想點改，其實達到差唔多既效果就可以架啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>感謝 連登 管理員</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f9bd78102ec4c3f2e61bc5b8ae692517d53f7c02","tid":1380474,"uid":18735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"三毛洗正皮點計？"},{"pid":"ab58825b89cdee286e8389ab358cbed6ed9e8583","tid":1380474,"uid":293246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9bd78102ec4c3f2e61bc5b8ae692517d53f7c02","tid":1380474,"uid":18735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"三毛洗正皮點計？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"佢洗正評，都係為左貼Post，騙風向，<br />\n到時大家知咩事，一人一負評，已經迅間令佢 評價跌到谷底"},{"pid":"58379f91288939bc726f094047e4354663dcf8d7","tid":1380474,"uid":28558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy